Package sSquare

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Server This class contains main method need to be executed on server first. It creates 2 windows which contain captured video and forground detecton window. It opens 4 ports on machine which will be used by traffic lights to connect to server.  
    TCounter It is class used by Server. It contains methods to calculates time, Background Substraction, white pixel calculation and percentage calculation.  
    TLx There are 4 TL classes namely TL1, TL2, TL3, TL4 these classes are deployed on traffic lights which will contact Server class via sockets for data transmission and reception including time and status data.
